1
00:00:00,234 --> 00:00:02,203
♪

2
00:00:08,342 --> 00:00:10,344
( Singing in Japanese )

3
00:00:45,979 --> 00:00:49,916
Joseph: Well, I hate to say it,
but it’s too late for him.

4
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:53,454
He’s got a few days
before he dies at most.

5
00:00:53,487 --> 00:00:56,623
Jotaro, this is not your fault.
Trust me.

6
00:00:56,657 --> 00:00:59,827
Do you want to know why this man
swore his allegiance to dio

7
00:00:59,860 --> 00:01:02,896
and came to your school
to kill you?

8
00:01:02,930 --> 00:01:06,400
Look right here,
and I will show you!

9
00:01:06,433 --> 00:01:07,634
Jotaro: What is that?

10
00:01:07,668 --> 00:01:10,471
It looks like a spider
or a piece of flesh.

11
00:01:10,504 --> 00:01:13,974
That’s it? Is that what made him
swear allegiance to dio?

12
00:01:14,007 --> 00:01:17,344
Avdol: Yes, it’s a flesh bud
formed from dio’s cells.

13
00:01:17,377 --> 00:01:19,546
It connects directly
to the boy’s brain.

14
00:01:20,848 --> 00:01:24,452
Flesh buds are small,
but they have the power

15
00:01:24,484 --> 00:01:27,854
to influence a person’s
thoughts and actions.

16
00:01:27,888 --> 00:01:30,324
Joseph: Simply put,
that bud stirs him

17
00:01:30,357 --> 00:01:33,393
and awakens a certain feeling
far beyond his control.

18
00:01:33,427 --> 00:01:35,663
- ( Jotaro gasps )
- Joseph: Charisma!

19
00:01:35,696 --> 00:01:36,931
The sheer emotive power

20
00:01:36,964 --> 00:01:39,667
that drives a soldier
to follow a dictator

21
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:42,703
or a believer to put his faith
in a corrupt cult.

22
00:01:42,736 --> 00:01:44,371
This young man revered dio,

23
00:01:44,404 --> 00:01:46,706
and that’s why
he swore allegiance to him!

24
00:01:49,042 --> 00:01:52,012
Dio knows how to wield
the power of charisma,

25
00:01:52,045 --> 00:01:55,448
which means there will be others
he will try to influence.

26
00:01:55,482 --> 00:01:58,452
He ordered this young man,
kakyoin here, to kill us,

27
00:01:58,485 --> 00:02:00,554
and he won’t stop until he has.

28
00:02:00,587 --> 00:02:01,988
Jotaro: So remove the bud.

29
00:02:02,022 --> 00:02:04,057
Joseph: No.
The brain is very delicate.

30
00:02:04,091 --> 00:02:05,726
If he even twitches
while we extract it,

31
00:02:05,759 --> 00:02:07,961
it could cause brain damage.

32
00:02:07,995 --> 00:02:09,763
( Kakyoin gasps )

33
00:02:09,796 --> 00:02:11,398
Avdol: Jojo...

34
00:02:11,431 --> 00:02:13,533
I need to tell you something.

35
00:02:13,567 --> 00:02:17,037
Four months ago, while I
was still there in Cairo...

36
00:02:18,071 --> 00:02:19,039
( Groans )

37
00:02:19,072 --> 00:02:21,007
I encountered dio!

38
00:02:21,041 --> 00:02:22,576
( Jotaro gasps )

39
00:02:22,609 --> 00:02:24,911
♪

40
00:02:24,945 --> 00:02:27,448
Avdol: I am a fortuneteller
by trade.

41
00:02:27,481 --> 00:02:30,718
I have a shop
in a souk called Khan khalili.

42
00:02:30,751 --> 00:02:33,621
It was a full moon that night,

43
00:02:33,654 --> 00:02:35,956
and there he was.

44
00:02:35,989 --> 00:02:37,357
( Gasps )

45
00:02:39,927 --> 00:02:42,363
He just stood
at the top of the stairs

46
00:02:42,396 --> 00:02:43,931
outside my shop silently,

47
00:02:43,964 --> 00:02:47,935
with eyes so cold it felt like
he was invading my heart,

48
00:02:47,968 --> 00:02:51,538
golden hair,
and translucent alabaster skin,

49
00:02:51,572 --> 00:02:53,941
but, most of all,
a dubious sensuality,

50
00:02:53,974 --> 00:02:56,510
the kind you
wouldn’t expect from a man.

51
00:02:56,543 --> 00:02:58,879
Because Mr. Joestar
had warned me about him,

52
00:02:58,912 --> 00:03:01,114
I knew exactly who he was,

53
00:03:01,148 --> 00:03:04,518
dio resurrected from
the depths of the Atlantic!

54
00:03:04,551 --> 00:03:07,454
Dio: I hear
you have a special ability

55
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:09,923
beyond that
of an ordinary person.

56
00:03:09,957 --> 00:03:11,959
This true?

57
00:03:11,992 --> 00:03:15,696
It would please me if you’d
Grant me a small demonstration.

58
00:03:15,729 --> 00:03:16,697
( Slurps )

59
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:18,098
( Avdol shuddering )

60
00:03:18,131 --> 00:03:21,901
It was then that I found him
to be truly terrifying.

61
00:03:21,935 --> 00:03:25,639
Every word he spoke
calmed my heart.

62
00:03:25,672 --> 00:03:28,041
The dangerous sweetness
in his voice

63
00:03:28,075 --> 00:03:32,079
is precisely
what makes him so terrifying!

64
00:03:32,112 --> 00:03:35,449
Dio avdol, come here.

65
00:03:37,518 --> 00:03:39,653
( Avdol screams )

66
00:03:39,686 --> 00:03:41,721
♪

67
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,458
I ran for my life.

68
00:03:44,491 --> 00:03:46,393
I didn’t dare
think of fighting him.

69
00:03:46,426 --> 00:03:48,161
I was very fortunate.

70
00:03:48,195 --> 00:03:49,697
Because I had
prior knowledge of dio,

71
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:51,865
I was able to realize
who he was.

72
00:03:51,899 --> 00:03:53,634
I immediately jumped
out the window.

73
00:03:53,667 --> 00:03:54,968
That souk is a labyrinth,

74
00:03:55,002 --> 00:03:57,505
but I know it
like the back of my hand,

75
00:03:57,538 --> 00:03:59,573
and thanks to that,
I was able to escape.

76
00:04:01,008 --> 00:04:04,178
Otherwise, I would have
ended up like this young man,

77
00:04:04,211 --> 00:04:06,680
another follower
controlled by a flesh bud.

78
00:04:06,713 --> 00:04:09,516
Joseph: You would have died
a few years later,

79
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:11,452
with your brain
completely devoured.

80
00:04:11,485 --> 00:04:13,187
Jotaro: Died?

81
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:15,155
Let’s not jump the gun.

82
00:04:15,189 --> 00:04:20,161
Kakyoin’s not in great shape,
but he’s not dead yet!

83
00:04:20,194 --> 00:04:21,796
♪

84
00:04:21,829 --> 00:04:25,433
I’ll pull it out with my stand.

85
00:04:25,465 --> 00:04:27,133
- ( Avdol gasps )
- Joseph: No, jotaro! Stop!

86
00:04:27,167 --> 00:04:29,636
Jotaro: Old man, just back off.

87
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:32,206
I can remove this thing
without damaging his brain.

88
00:04:32,239 --> 00:04:35,876
If my stand has the precision
to catch a speeding bullet,

89
00:04:35,909 --> 00:04:38,011
- then it can also do this.
- Joseph: Listen!

90
00:04:38,045 --> 00:04:39,847
That flesh bud is alive.
Can’t you see?

91
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:43,484
Part of that flesh bud lives
outside his body for a reason.

92
00:04:43,517 --> 00:04:44,752
Even a skilled surgeon

93
00:04:44,785 --> 00:04:46,654
can’t remove it
without serious damage!

94
00:04:46,687 --> 00:04:47,888
Shit.

95
00:04:47,921 --> 00:04:49,723
Avdol: It just sunk itself
into his flesh.

96
00:04:49,756 --> 00:04:51,758
This is bad.
You have to let go, jojo!

97
00:04:51,792 --> 00:04:53,827
Joseph: It can infiltrate
anyone’s brain

98
00:04:53,861 --> 00:04:55,096
who dares try to remove it!

99
00:04:55,128 --> 00:04:56,129
( Jotaro grunts )

100
00:04:58,131 --> 00:05:00,700
Kakyoin: Why are you--

101
00:05:00,734 --> 00:05:02,536
I would try not to move.

102
00:05:02,569 --> 00:05:05,138
If I mess this up,
your brain is fried.

103
00:05:05,172 --> 00:05:06,740
♪

104
00:05:11,512 --> 00:05:12,513
Avdol: No, jojo!

105
00:05:12,546 --> 00:05:13,847
It’s ready reached your neck!

106
00:05:13,881 --> 00:05:15,850
- You have to let go!
- Joseph: Hold on, avdol.

107
00:05:15,883 --> 00:05:18,152
My grandson is very impressive.

108
00:05:18,185 --> 00:05:20,854
That thing’s made it
halfway through his body,

109
00:05:20,888 --> 00:05:22,590
and yet he’s
still completely calm,

110
00:05:22,623 --> 00:05:25,826
not even a tremble
from either him or his stand.

111
00:05:25,859 --> 00:05:27,894
He can move
with more precision and strength

112
00:05:27,928 --> 00:05:30,097
than I ever anticipated!

113
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:31,698
( Kakyoin shudders )

114
00:05:34,735 --> 00:05:36,570
Avdol: He did it.

115
00:05:36,603 --> 00:05:38,605
( Stand yelling )

116
00:05:42,643 --> 00:05:44,578
Joseph: Overdrive!

117
00:05:52,786 --> 00:05:53,787
( Kakyoin gasps )

118
00:05:57,658 --> 00:05:58,792
Tell me,

119
00:05:58,825 --> 00:06:01,895
why did you risk your life
to save me?

120
00:06:01,929 --> 00:06:02,897
( Holly gasps )

121
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:04,832
♪

122
00:06:10,204 --> 00:06:11,772
Jotaro: Don’t know.

123
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:16,009
I don’t really have
an answer for that.

124
00:06:23,784 --> 00:06:28,222
Holly: Jotaro,
I see right through you.

125
00:06:31,825 --> 00:06:33,627
All done.

126
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,962
Kakyoin: Thank you
for everything.

127
00:06:35,996 --> 00:06:37,798
Holly: So it’s kakyoin, was it?

128
00:06:37,831 --> 00:06:41,034
You need to rest for a while.
Why don’t you stay here tonight?

129
00:06:41,068 --> 00:06:42,236
Kakyoin: Huh? No, i--

130
00:06:42,269 --> 00:06:43,937
Holly: Papa,
go and get his futon ready.

131
00:06:43,971 --> 00:06:46,073
Joseph: Hmm?
Why do I have to do it?!

132
00:06:46,106 --> 00:06:49,109
I’ve never even liked the idea
of sleeping on the damn floor!

133
00:06:49,142 --> 00:06:52,646
In fact, that futon in my room,
replace it with a real bed!

134
00:06:52,679 --> 00:06:54,915
Holly: No way.
You’re in Japan now, papa,

135
00:06:54,948 --> 00:06:57,317
and here in Japan,
we sleep on the floor.

136
00:06:57,351 --> 00:07:00,120
And i’d prefer if you
call me seiko here.

137
00:07:00,153 --> 00:07:01,621
Joseph: What?!

138
00:07:01,655 --> 00:07:04,057
Holly: The Japanese
also have a word for holy.

139
00:07:04,091 --> 00:07:06,126
Here, the word for it
is "seinaru,"

140
00:07:06,159 --> 00:07:09,796
so that’s why all my friends
call me seiko here. ( Giggles )

141
00:07:09,830 --> 00:07:11,231
Joseph: What the hell is that?!

142
00:07:11,265 --> 00:07:13,667
Holly’s a beautiful name!
I gave it to you mys--

143
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:16,069
Holly: If you don’t refer to me
as seiko, I won’t answer.

144
00:07:16,103 --> 00:07:17,271
Joseph: Holly!

145
00:07:17,304 --> 00:07:18,672
Holly:
How’s the pain, kakyoin, bad?

146
00:07:18,705 --> 00:07:19,873
Kakyoin: No. I’m fine.

147
00:07:19,907 --> 00:07:21,709
- Joseph: Holly!
- Jotaro: Gimme a break.

148
00:07:21,742 --> 00:07:23,377
Holly: All right, kakyoin, let’s
get you out of that uniform.

149
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:24,878
- ( Kakyoin gasps )
- Holly: Go on. Take it off.

150
00:07:24,912 --> 00:07:27,114
- Joseph: Holly!
- Holly: Did I hear something?

151
00:07:27,147 --> 00:07:30,417
( Joseph screams )

152
00:07:32,119 --> 00:07:34,121
( Birds chirping )

153
00:07:35,422 --> 00:07:36,924
Joseph: Holly!

154
00:07:36,957 --> 00:07:39,259
Hey, Holly!

155
00:07:39,293 --> 00:07:41,662
Come on! Where are you?

156
00:07:41,695 --> 00:07:43,864
I want you to look at this.

157
00:07:43,897 --> 00:07:47,134
You gave me jotaro’s pants.

158
00:07:47,167 --> 00:07:49,169
Where the heck are mine?

159
00:07:49,203 --> 00:07:52,840
They’re the right size and all,
but i’m not wearin’ these.

160
00:07:52,873 --> 00:07:54,274
Hey, Holly!

161
00:07:56,710 --> 00:08:00,314
Oh, i’m supposed to call her
seiko, or she won’t answer me.

162
00:08:00,347 --> 00:08:02,015
Hmm.

163
00:08:02,049 --> 00:08:04,318
No! My daughter has one name.

164
00:08:04,351 --> 00:08:06,687
Answer me, Holly!

165
00:08:09,056 --> 00:08:11,225
Jotaro: All right,
time for school.

166
00:08:11,258 --> 00:08:13,894
I’m actually gonna go. Hmm.

167
00:08:13,927 --> 00:08:15,729
That’s weird.

168
00:08:17,197 --> 00:08:21,001
Holly: Here is
your goodbye kiss.

169
00:08:21,034 --> 00:08:24,671
Jotaro: That’s usually
how my mornings play out.

170
00:08:24,705 --> 00:08:26,473
♪

171
00:08:30,911 --> 00:08:33,380
( Kakyoin gasps )

172
00:08:41,922 --> 00:08:43,090
Avdol: Huh?

173
00:09:04,845 --> 00:09:06,480
No. Mrs. Kujo!

174
00:09:07,481 --> 00:09:09,984
Mrs. Kujo, please, wake up.

175
00:09:11,385 --> 00:09:13,854
- ( Holly panting )
- Avdol: She’s burning up.

176
00:09:13,887 --> 00:09:15,455
Is she sick?

177
00:09:15,489 --> 00:09:16,957
( Holly gasps )

178
00:09:16,990 --> 00:09:19,125
Avdol: No. This can’t be.

179
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:21,194
Mrs. Kujo, please.

180
00:09:21,228 --> 00:09:22,763
Forgive me.

181
00:09:24,832 --> 00:09:27,401
No. How did this happen?

182
00:09:27,434 --> 00:09:29,269
It’s transparent.

183
00:09:29,303 --> 00:09:31,405
She has a stand.

184
00:09:31,438 --> 00:09:35,242
Mrs. Kujo has materialized
her own stand!

185
00:09:40,881 --> 00:09:43,617
Well,

186
00:09:43,650 --> 00:09:45,085
but this high fever.

187
00:09:45,118 --> 00:09:48,288
The stand
is doing damage to her.

188
00:09:48,322 --> 00:09:50,958
We were all so relieved
that dio’s body

189
00:09:50,991 --> 00:09:53,227
had only affected
jojo and Mr. Joestar.

190
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:55,963
We were so certain
Mrs. Kujo was fine.

191
00:09:55,996 --> 00:09:59,266
But that’s just
what we wanted to believe.

192
00:09:59,299 --> 00:10:01,368
It’s impossible
for her to escape that.

193
00:10:01,401 --> 00:10:04,170
As long as she has
joestar blood in her veins,

194
00:10:04,204 --> 00:10:06,973
there will inevitably
be an effect from dio.

195
00:10:07,007 --> 00:10:08,041
But still...

196
00:10:09,176 --> 00:10:10,644
A stand is controlled

197
00:10:10,677 --> 00:10:13,013
by an individual’s
own mental strength,

198
00:10:13,046 --> 00:10:15,849
and they move according to
that person’s fighting instinct.

199
00:10:17,017 --> 00:10:19,720
Mrs. Kujo is
a kind and peaceful woman

200
00:10:19,753 --> 00:10:21,922
who doesn’t have the power
to resist dio’s curse.

201
00:10:21,955 --> 00:10:26,126
She doesn’t have the strength
she needs to control her stand.

202
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:29,162
This has to be why her stand
is making her so ill.

203
00:10:29,196 --> 00:10:30,998
It’s acting against her,
not with her.

204
00:10:32,032 --> 00:10:33,667
It’s only getting worse.

205
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:34,968
This is very bad.

206
00:10:35,002 --> 00:10:37,438
At this rate, she’ll die.

207
00:10:37,471 --> 00:10:39,807
She’ll be overcome!

208
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,108
( Gasps )

209
00:10:44,378 --> 00:10:46,780
Joseph: She has a stand?

210
00:10:49,216 --> 00:10:51,985
( Shudders ) Holly.

211
00:10:52,019 --> 00:10:54,788
( Jotaro gasps )

212
00:10:54,821 --> 00:11:01,394
Joseph: Nooooo!

213
00:11:01,428 --> 00:11:04,865
( Sobs )

214
00:11:04,898 --> 00:11:07,934
This is the one thing
I feared the most.

215
00:11:07,968 --> 00:11:11,038
This is very last thing
I ever wanted to happen.

216
00:11:11,071 --> 00:11:14,341
My daughter
has developed a stand as well.

217
00:11:14,374 --> 00:11:17,944
I’ve always known
she’s too weak.

218
00:11:17,978 --> 00:11:19,346
She can’t withstand it.

219
00:11:19,379 --> 00:11:22,716
I knew if this day came,
it would destroy her.

220
00:11:22,749 --> 00:11:27,053
She doesn’t have the strength
needed to repel dio’s curse.

221
00:11:27,087 --> 00:11:28,855
( Cries )

222
00:11:28,889 --> 00:11:31,058
( Winces )

223
00:11:32,926 --> 00:11:35,262
Jotaro: Tell me. What we can do?

224
00:11:35,295 --> 00:11:37,297
♪

225
00:11:40,234 --> 00:11:41,268
Joseph: Okay.

226
00:11:41,301 --> 00:11:43,737
To start, we must find dio.

227
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:46,006
The only way to break this curse

228
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:48,308
is to find dio and kill him!

229
00:11:51,945 --> 00:11:53,213
Finding him is the problem.

230
00:11:53,247 --> 00:11:55,249
No matter how many times I try,

231
00:11:55,282 --> 00:11:57,184
he’s always hiding
in the darkness.

232
00:11:57,217 --> 00:12:01,221
In every spirit photo I take,
the background is black.

233
00:12:01,255 --> 00:12:04,291
We won’t be able to locate him
with my photographs.

234
00:12:04,324 --> 00:12:07,394
Avdol: We’ve used various
methods to try and analyze them,

235
00:12:07,427 --> 00:12:10,864
but with this darkness,
we always come up with nothing.

236
00:12:10,898 --> 00:12:14,335
Jotaro: Hey, you should have
mentioned this to me sooner.

237
00:12:14,368 --> 00:12:17,538
Let me look.
I might be able to find out...

238
00:12:19,373 --> 00:12:21,508
What’s hiding in that darkness.

239
00:12:27,347 --> 00:12:29,850
It’s found something
within the shadows.

240
00:12:31,585 --> 00:12:34,021
My stand
can move accurately enough

241
00:12:34,054 --> 00:12:37,291
to pull a flesh bud
from someone’s brain

242
00:12:37,324 --> 00:12:39,159
and catch a bullet.

243
00:12:40,327 --> 00:12:42,229
Let’s have it sketch
what it sees.

244
00:12:49,002 --> 00:12:51,004
Joseph: Hmm.

245
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,375
( Jotaro gasps )

246
00:12:54,408 --> 00:12:56,110
Avdol: No way!

247
00:12:56,143 --> 00:12:58,178
It saw a fly through all that!

248
00:12:58,212 --> 00:13:00,881
Joseph: Yeah, but how in
the hell is a fly gonna help us?

249
00:13:00,914 --> 00:13:03,049
Avdol: Wait a second.
I’ve seen this fly before.

250
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,217
Joseph: What?

251
00:13:04,251 --> 00:13:05,552
Avdol: Do you have
an encyclopedia?

252
00:13:05,586 --> 00:13:06,921
Jotaro: We do have a library.

253
00:13:06,954 --> 00:13:08,155
Avdol: Let me have the sketch.

254
00:13:08,188 --> 00:13:10,624
I’ll do some research!

255
00:13:12,860 --> 00:13:15,029
( Holly moans )

256
00:13:15,062 --> 00:13:16,931
Joseph: Hmm. Oh, Holly.

257
00:13:16,964 --> 00:13:19,300
Holly: Papa, I...

258
00:13:19,333 --> 00:13:20,434
Joseph: You just rest.

259
00:13:20,467 --> 00:13:22,469
Jotaro, get some water.

260
00:13:24,872 --> 00:13:26,874
♪

261
00:13:35,349 --> 00:13:36,517
Avdol: Hmm.

262
00:13:39,019 --> 00:13:41,522
You seem to be doing well.

263
00:13:41,555 --> 00:13:44,425
Sorry, but i’m
a little busy right now.

264
00:13:44,458 --> 00:13:48,462
Kakyoin: Can your own stand
really do that to you, kill you?

265
00:13:48,495 --> 00:13:50,230
Avdol: Yes.

266
00:13:50,264 --> 00:13:54,034
I have seen far too many people
suffer exactly that same fate.

267
00:13:54,067 --> 00:13:55,335
Kakyoin: Really?

268
00:13:55,369 --> 00:13:57,504
Avdol: It’s limited
to her back right now,

269
00:13:57,538 --> 00:14:00,307
but that stand will grow
like a fiendish vine,

270
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:03,043
and it won’t stop
until her whole body

271
00:14:03,076 --> 00:14:04,377
is overtaken and bound.

272
00:14:04,411 --> 00:14:08,181
Her fever will rise,
and her illness will worsen,

273
00:14:08,215 --> 00:14:13,053
she’ll fall into a coma
and never wake up, and then...

274
00:14:13,086 --> 00:14:14,187
She’ll die.

275
00:14:14,221 --> 00:14:15,389
( Kakyoin gasps )

276
00:14:15,422 --> 00:14:17,591
Avdol: Your average person
would see this

277
00:14:17,624 --> 00:14:19,459
as some rare and unknown disease

278
00:14:19,493 --> 00:14:23,197
that no doctor in the world
would be able to treat.

279
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:29,002
And normally neither you nor I
could do anything about it.

280
00:14:29,036 --> 00:14:30,571
( Kakyoin shudders )

281
00:14:30,604 --> 00:14:32,606
Avdol: But there is still hope.

282
00:14:32,639 --> 00:14:36,476
It will take 50 days for
her body to reach that state.

283
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:39,580
We just have to find
and defeat dio before that.

284
00:14:39,613 --> 00:14:43,117
If we can sever the link
her stand has with dio,

285
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:45,152
we can save her.

286
00:14:47,621 --> 00:14:48,689
( Holly sighs )

287
00:14:48,722 --> 00:14:50,624
Thank you for that, jotaro.

288
00:14:50,657 --> 00:14:53,393
I wonder what it was
that came over me today.

289
00:14:53,427 --> 00:14:56,130
I can’t believe I had a fever
and passed out like that.

290
00:14:56,163 --> 00:14:57,297
But that said...

291
00:14:57,331 --> 00:14:59,133
Jotaro: Because it’s
on her back,

292
00:14:59,166 --> 00:15:00,401
she can’t see it.

293
00:15:00,434 --> 00:15:02,670
She has no idea
what’s happened.

294
00:15:02,703 --> 00:15:05,339
Jotaro: Well, you gave us
quite a scare, Holly.

295
00:15:05,372 --> 00:15:08,575
Hey, now that you’re up,
why don’t you brush your teeth?

296
00:15:08,609 --> 00:15:09,977
Say, "ahh."

297
00:15:10,010 --> 00:15:11,011
Holly: Ahh.

298
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:15,448
Joseph: And let’s
get that face clean.

299
00:15:15,482 --> 00:15:18,051
We’ll tidy up your hair
while we’re at it.

300
00:15:18,085 --> 00:15:20,387
Then let’s take care
of those nails.

301
00:15:21,421 --> 00:15:22,555
Ahh...

302
00:15:22,589 --> 00:15:24,257
Holly: Ahh.

303
00:15:25,259 --> 00:15:26,560
Oh.

304
00:15:26,593 --> 00:15:29,429
Papa, will you help me
change my underwear, too?

305
00:15:29,463 --> 00:15:30,664
- Joseph: Huh?
- ( Holly laughs )

306
00:15:30,697 --> 00:15:34,434
Just relax. I was only kidding.

307
00:15:34,468 --> 00:15:35,636
All right, then.

308
00:15:35,669 --> 00:15:37,204
What do you want
for dinner, jotaro?

309
00:15:37,237 --> 00:15:38,638
- Joseph: Hey.
- Jotaro: Don’t move!

310
00:15:38,672 --> 00:15:40,641
- You just stay in bed.
- Joseph: Huh?

311
00:15:42,276 --> 00:15:45,479
Jotaro: I just meant
you should stay put,

312
00:15:45,512 --> 00:15:47,447
at least
until your fever breaks.

313
00:15:47,481 --> 00:15:50,684
Now be quiet, and get better.

314
00:15:52,019 --> 00:15:53,220
Joseph: He’s right.

315
00:15:53,253 --> 00:15:54,321
Rest.

316
00:15:54,354 --> 00:15:56,356
Holly: Heh. Okay.

317
00:15:58,492 --> 00:16:00,694
I kinda like this.

318
00:16:00,727 --> 00:16:03,263
Everyone’s so nice
when I get sick.

319
00:16:03,297 --> 00:16:07,468
Having a little cold
isn’t so bad from time to time.

320
00:16:07,501 --> 00:16:08,569
( Sighs )

321
00:16:08,602 --> 00:16:10,204
Joseph: What? Holly!

322
00:16:10,237 --> 00:16:12,139
Say something.

323
00:16:12,172 --> 00:16:14,675
She--she lost
consciousness again.

324
00:16:14,708 --> 00:16:16,076
Come on.

325
00:16:16,109 --> 00:16:17,744
She was acting fine,

326
00:16:17,778 --> 00:16:19,747
but this fever is so bad.

327
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:21,482
It’s spiked.

328
00:16:21,515 --> 00:16:23,417
She was
just putting on a good front.

329
00:16:23,450 --> 00:16:26,219
I know she didn’t say anything,

330
00:16:26,253 --> 00:16:30,290
but my daughter is
definitely aware of her stand.

331
00:16:30,324 --> 00:16:35,196
She was doing her best just now
to try and hide it from us.

332
00:16:35,229 --> 00:16:39,767
My guess is that she didn’t
want us to worry about her.

333
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:43,370
My daughter’s
always been like that.

334
00:16:44,805 --> 00:16:47,174
Avdol: Mr. Joestar,
i’ve found it.

335
00:16:47,207 --> 00:16:48,775
I know where that fly is from.

336
00:16:51,278 --> 00:16:53,313
It’s this one.

337
00:16:53,347 --> 00:16:55,149
Narrator: The nile tsetse fly,

338
00:16:55,182 --> 00:16:58,485
a bloodsucking insect prevalent
in the nile river basin

339
00:16:58,519 --> 00:17:01,222
the tsetse genus
includes a striped species

340
00:17:01,255 --> 00:17:03,257
known as the aswan tsetse fly.

341
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:04,792
Joseph: Egypt.

342
00:17:04,825 --> 00:17:07,294
Avdol: And we’ve narrowed it
down to the aswan region.

343
00:17:07,327 --> 00:17:08,461
Dio is there.

344
00:17:08,495 --> 00:17:10,464
Kakyoin: So he is
in Egypt after all.

345
00:17:10,497 --> 00:17:11,832
Jotaro: Kakyoin.

346
00:17:11,865 --> 00:17:14,201
Joseph: What do
you mean by that?

347
00:17:14,234 --> 00:17:15,469
Kakyoin: The flesh bud

348
00:17:15,502 --> 00:17:17,471
was planted into my brain
three months ago.

349
00:17:17,504 --> 00:17:18,772
That’s when I met dio.

350
00:17:18,805 --> 00:17:21,641
I was on a trip
with my family in Egypt.

351
00:17:21,675 --> 00:17:23,577
We were there touring the nile.

352
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:25,412
Avdol: You were in Egypt, too.

353
00:17:25,445 --> 00:17:26,846
It seems for some reason,

354
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:30,183
dio wants to remain
in that area.

355
00:17:30,217 --> 00:17:32,186
Kakyoin:
So when are we leaving?

356
00:17:32,219 --> 00:17:34,188
Because i’ll be going with you.

357
00:17:34,221 --> 00:17:35,189
( Both gasp )

358
00:17:35,222 --> 00:17:36,757
Jotaro: Seriously?

359
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:38,859
Why would you want to do that?

360
00:17:38,892 --> 00:17:41,294
Kakyoin: To be
completely honest,

361
00:17:41,328 --> 00:17:43,831
I have no idea
why I want to either.

362
00:17:43,864 --> 00:17:46,300
It’s just something
I feel compelled to do.

363
00:17:47,334 --> 00:17:48,702
( Jotaro scoffs )

364
00:17:48,735 --> 00:17:52,172
Kakyoin: Let’s just say
that you opened my eyes.

365
00:17:52,206 --> 00:17:53,708
It’s that simple.

366
00:18:00,581 --> 00:18:03,651
Joseph: Holly, we’re gonna
save you, no matter what.

367
00:18:03,684 --> 00:18:05,119
You have my word.

368
00:18:05,152 --> 00:18:08,489
There’s nothing
for you to worry about.

369
00:18:08,522 --> 00:18:11,725
We are gonna make you better.
I promise.

370
00:18:11,758 --> 00:18:14,494
Just take it easy, and rest.

371
00:18:16,763 --> 00:18:20,300
Kakyoin: Jojo’s mother,
Holly, has the ability

372
00:18:20,334 --> 00:18:23,571
to calm a person’s soul
and put their minds at ease.

373
00:18:23,604 --> 00:18:26,474
People feel relaxed
just by being near her.

374
00:18:26,507 --> 00:18:30,578
This may sound strange,
but if I ever fall in love,

375
00:18:30,611 --> 00:18:32,746
i’d want it to be
with someone like her.

376
00:18:32,779 --> 00:18:34,748
I’d feel the need
to protect her.

377
00:18:34,781 --> 00:18:39,619
I’d do anything to see her
feeling better and smiling.

378
00:18:39,653 --> 00:18:41,421
Avdol: Indeed.

379
00:18:42,456 --> 00:18:43,924
Joseph: There’s no time!

380
00:18:43,957 --> 00:18:45,926
We leave immediately!

381
00:18:45,959 --> 00:18:47,961
♪

382
00:18:52,266 --> 00:18:53,768
We can trust ’em.

383
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,703
They’re doctors from
the speedwagon foundation.

384
00:18:56,737 --> 00:18:58,439
They’re going to stay with her

385
00:18:58,472 --> 00:19:01,308
and take care of Holly
around the clock.

386
00:19:01,341 --> 00:19:03,844
Avdol: Jojo, since I am
a fortuneteller by trade,

387
00:19:03,877 --> 00:19:06,279
i’d like to name your stand
before we go.

388
00:19:06,313 --> 00:19:07,481
Joseph: Huh? Name it?

389
00:19:07,514 --> 00:19:10,417
Avdol: With the tarot,
the cards of fate.

390
00:19:10,450 --> 00:19:13,286
Do not look, but let chance
guide your choice.

391
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:16,356
It will not only suggest to us
your destiny,

392
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:19,293
but also the abilities
of your stand.

393
00:19:24,832 --> 00:19:26,634
The star card.

394
00:19:26,667 --> 00:19:28,936
I shall name your stand...

395
00:19:28,969 --> 00:19:31,738
Star platinum!

396
00:19:31,772 --> 00:19:33,507
Narrator: Jotaro kujo.

397
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:35,475
Stand name, star platinum.

398
00:19:35,509 --> 00:19:38,879
Abilities, precision in movement
and extreme strength.

399
00:19:38,912 --> 00:19:40,313
Joseph joestar.

400
00:19:40,347 --> 00:19:41,915
Stand name, hermit purple.

401
00:19:41,949 --> 00:19:44,285
Abilities, spirit photography.

402
00:19:44,318 --> 00:19:45,619
Mohammed avdol.

403
00:19:45,652 --> 00:19:47,487
Stand name, magician’s red.

404
00:19:47,521 --> 00:19:49,556
Abilities, fire and heat.

405
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:50,858
Noriaki kakyoin.

406
00:19:50,891 --> 00:19:52,993
Stand name, hierophant green.

407
00:19:53,026 --> 00:19:55,529
Abilities,
remote stand manipulation

408
00:19:55,562 --> 00:19:56,696
and emerald splash.

409
00:19:56,730 --> 00:19:59,633
Joseph: All right, we’re off!

410
00:20:02,269 --> 00:20:03,937
Let’s hit the road.

411
00:20:06,874 --> 00:20:08,876
♪

412
00:20:21,021 --> 00:20:23,490
♪ All the old paintings
on the tomb ♪

413
