♪ they got the money on a bet

419
00:20:34,902 --> 00:20:36,270
♪ gold crocodiles

420
00:20:36,303 --> 00:20:37,604
♪ oh, whey, oh

421
00:20:37,638 --> 00:20:39,673
♪ they snap their teeth
on your cigarette ♪

422
