♪ whey, oh, whey, oh

424
00:20:44,311 --> 00:20:47,815
♪ ay, whey, oh, whey, oh

425
00:20:48,916 --> 00:20:51,552
♪ walk like an Egyptian

426
00:21:02,796 --> 00:21:05,499
♪ The blond waitresses
take their trays ♪

427
00:21:05,532 --> 00:21:07,601
♪ they spin around,
and they cross the floor ♪

428
00:21:07,634 --> 00:21:08,869
♪ they’ve got the moves

429
00:21:08,902 --> 00:21:09,870
♪ oh, whey, oh

430
00:21:09,903 --> 00:21:10,904
♪ you drop your drink

431
00:21:10,938 --> 00:21:12,406
♪ then they bring you more

432
