♪ all the kids
in the marketplace say ♪

438
00:21:23,784 --> 00:21:25,986
♪ whey, oh, whey, oh

439
00:21:26,019 --> 00:21:30,790
♪ ay, whey, oh, whey, oh

440
00:21:30,824 --> 00:21:33,894
♪ walk like an Egyptian

441
00:21:39,766 --> 00:21:41,768
♪

442
00:21:59,152 --> 00:22:03,890
Dio: As I thought,
they found out where I am.

443
00:22:05,792 --> 00:22:08,561
So then, will you come to Egypt,

444
00:22:08,595 --> 00:22:11,832
Joseph and jotaro?

445
00:22:12,933 --> 00:22:14,768
( Joseph gasps )

446
00:22:14,801 --> 00:22:18,838
He saw us. I definitely felt
dio looking at us just now.

447
00:22:18,872 --> 00:22:19,840
Jotaro: Yeah.

448
00:22:19,873 --> 00:22:21,375
Joseph: Be careful.

449
00:22:21,408 --> 00:22:27,147
A new stand user
could already be on this plane.

450
00:22:28,415 --> 00:22:30,183
( Insect buzzing )

